Update the user profile page to include the following:

Display the user's name, email, the number of posts by the user, and the number of comments by the user.
Display the name of the user with the greatest number of comments and their respective number of comments.
Include a "delete" button that can be used to delete the user, but only if the user has no posts and comments.

    - Coding Standards Section:

